  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate whether dietary nitrate supplementation could
      improve the plasma nitrate levels for nasopharyngeal carcinoma patients receiving concurrent
      chemo-radiation therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Twenty patients diagnosed as nasopharyngeal carcinoma will be recruited. A 70 ml beetroot
      juice containing 0.45g nitrate or placebo will be provided to the patients for 7 days at the
      end of the radiotherapy . The plasma nitrate levels will be determined before radiotherapy,
      before intervention and after intervention.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
