  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with newly diagnosed stages III-IVb (UICC 2002) nasopharyngeal carcinomas,
             will be recruited.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with local invasion or metastatic foci in salivary glands, detected by MRI
             and PET-CT prior to treatment, were excluded, as were patients suffering from
             diseases, such as Sjogren's syndrome, or with a history of surgery to major salivary
             glands, or prior head and neck radiotherapy.
      </textblock>
